Sphere: Divine Sphere<br/><br/>
<br/><br/>
Usage cast curse (target)<br/><br/>
<br/>
This spell brings down the negative divine forces of the world upon its<br/>
target.  If cast upon a character the target's strength,<br/>
dexterity, divine<br/>
and especially magic potential is reduced for a<br/>
while.<br/>
<br/><br/><br/>
If cast upon an object it will become cursed and the next person equipping<br/>
it will be unable to unequip it for a while.<br/>
